:

*Zaljubljena* devojka je plakala zbog nedostatka pažnje. (The infatuated girl was crying due to lack of attention.)

Bio je *zaljubljen* u nju već od prvog susreta. (He had been infatuated with her since the first meeting.)

*Zaljubljivanje* je za nju bilo jedino zanimanje. (Falling in love was her only hobby.)

*Zaljubljenost* u njega bila je očigledna. (Her infatuation with him was obvious.)

Ona se često prepuštala *zaljubljivanju*. (She often indulged in falling in love.)